# Emitted crosswalk artifacts are byte-compared by
# `build_crosswalk.py --check`. Pin to LF so the drift gate is
# deterministic on every platform -- a Windows checkout
# (core.autocrlf=true) would otherwise rewrite them to CRLF and
# the gate would false-fail even when mappings.yaml is correct.
crosswalk.csv  text eol=lf
crosswalk.md   text eol=lf
crosswalk.json text eol=lf
